topup.title: Walleta Keesa Guusso
topup.description: Walleta ka'amaa guussani foormii haattin guussa

q1.question: Walleta ka'amaa heexuwa akkami woyya?
q1.answer: Saphicha ayyantta goppetta, walleta kee ka'amaa woyine amanchisuwa.

q2.question: Walleta kiya balansi gaggabbisuwa tariika qaba'aa?
q2.answer: Woye, walleta ka'amaa gaggabbisu tariika male, akka account kee hojjatu malee tura.

q3.question: Walleta balansi account biraa geessu danda'aa?
q3.answer: Woye, walleta balansi gaggabbisu account woyna hin dabo. Account tokko qofan walleta tied.

hero.description: Aante online bittan xalaya bita hetticho xawusa. Xalayshuwo aba xaafote woynuwote. Iccuwa bita, doogidi qama!
aboutParagraph1: Campus Bites daggino uurrinsho barra darga coyi'ra gidoonsa uurrinshote woyite laalino gasho. Ninke uurrinshotaho coyi'ra darga hagiira, hagiira ikkanno mugga laasisa dandaanno.
aboutParagraph2: Ninke addasi uurrinshote lawonjesinni mugga laasisa dandaanno. Ninke campus olli mugga coyi'ro gasho, halaaleno Itoophiya mugga laasisa dandaanno.
aboutParagraph3: Ninke ammananno mugga laasisa dandaanno, darga ikkanno mugga laasisa dandaanno. Ninke Campus Bites uurrinshote mugga laasisa dandaanno, loosonna woyita ayirrasio dandaanno.
